{"tid":826500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"密斗貨車輾過打風垃圾 失事鏟上行人路撞巴士站","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T10:26:11.000Z","uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50b45b7adc85fefe4d9bdcbd5fd1f2549944b349","tid":826500,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"下午3時10分左右，一輛密斗貨車沿葵涌道往荃灣，至荔景邨風景樓外失事，鏟上行人路撞塌巴士站‧；幸當時沒有候車乘客，否則後果嚴重。事件中司機輕傷，報警求助。他事後稱，路面有打風吹下的障礙物，輾過時失事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/small/1537257283_0eff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Fsmall%2F1537257283_0eff.jpg&h=e1a14af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貨車失事撞塌巴士站。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/small/1537257791_e9a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Fsmall%2F1537257791_e9a7.jpg&h=78592976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士站損毀情況嚴重。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58695699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58695699&d=KStb7oAJy0v30uX54xUqckkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bf384229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58695699&h=c4340acc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58695699</a>"},{"pid":"3aa039583a1b5a7bf38a7a7d9e2bbebc696fa11a","tid":826500,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8306b79ef4844e8cfc7dbd5a580b622e7d9512c9","tid":826500,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"其實今日都應該停工停課<br />\n好多道路都塞塞地<img src=\"/assets/